<a href="https://openhatch.org/wiki/Special:UserLogout">https://openhatch.org/wiki/Special:UserLogout</a>

When I click on "Log in" in the upper-right corner, it sends me to:

<a href="https://openhatch.org/w/index.php?title=Special:UserLogin&amp;returnto=Special:UserLogout">https://openhatch.org/w/index.php?title=Special:UserLogin&amp;returnto=Special:UserLogout</a>

and then when the Django code passes us back to the wiki, MediaWiki immediately
logs me back out.</pre>
