   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>As per
<a href="http://irclogs.jackgrigg.com/irc.freenode.net/openhatch/2011-02-14#i_2538286">http://irclogs.jackgrigg.com/irc.freenode.net/openhatch/2011-02-14#i_2538286</a> and
onwards, the MediaWiki AuthDjango extension
(<a href="https://bitbucket.org/pythonian4000/django-mediawiki-authentication-by-user-id/src">https://bitbucket.org/pythonian4000/django-mediawiki-authentication-by-user-id/src</a>)
is ready to ship. the only remaining issue is that there are a number of
MediaWiki users that do not have corresponding Django usernames. Once a decision
is made over these (spam accounts deleted, other accounts secured or notified or
left etc.) then the extension will be activated and this feature will be done! ^_^</pre>
   </td>
  </tr>
 
 
