   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>I have added a site notice to the wiki (
<a href="http://openhatch.org/wiki/MediaWiki:Sitenotice">http://openhatch.org/wiki/MediaWiki:Sitenotice</a> ) that informs the users of the
pending change and to request a username change if needed.

On that note, links below are to MediaWiki extensions that allow user renaming
and merging, which we will need to add if any users require it:
<a href="http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Renameuser">http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:Renameuser</a>
<a href="http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:User_Merge_and_Delete">http://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Extension:User_Merge_and_Delete</a></pre>
